### ==========================================
### ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES (CHANGE YOUR IP HERE)
### ==========================================
@host = http://localhost:8080
### ==========================================
### 0. SETUP: CREATE OUR USERS
### ==========================================

### Create Dispatcher
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dave Dispatcher",
  "email": "dispatcher@mediflow.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "DISPATCHER"
}

### Create Paramedic
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pam Paramedic",
  "email": "paramedic@mediflow.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "PARAMEDIC"
}

### Create Admin
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Admin",
  "email": "admin@mediflow.com",
  "password": "adminpassword",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}


### ==========================================
### SCENARIO 1: Valid Dispatcher Creates Emergency
### ==========================================

### 1A. Login as Dispatcher (Copy the token from the response!)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dispatcher@mediflow.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 1B. Create Emergency (Paste token below)
POST {{host}}/api/emergency
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: {{$uuid}}
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJyb2xlIjoiRElTUEFUQ0hFUiIsInN1YiI6IjEiLCJpYXQiOjE3ODE1MTI0NzksImV4cCI6MTc4MTU5ODg3OX0.qb7R-idKG8OuKrtICcsGcvzOLVZN6wSnG2mIPrTtG4SAl_NR7W2mnU3AZwifHmSs

{
  "patientId": "PAT-98775",
  "severity": "CRITICAL",
  "latitude": 28.6139,
  "longitude": 77.2090
}


### ==========================================
### SCENARIO 2: Invalid JWT is Rejected
### ==========================================

### 2A. Attempt request with fake token
POST {{host}}/api/emergency
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: 123765
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.fake.token

### EXPECTED: 401 Unauthorized


### ==========================================
### SCENARIO 3: Paramedic Cannot Create Hospital
### ==========================================

### 3A. Login as Paramedic (Copy the token!)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "paramedic@mediflow.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3B. Attempt to access a restricted Admin endpoint
POST {{host}}/api/hospitals
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: 2398736
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJyb2xlIjoiUEFSQU1FRElDIiwic3ViIjoiMiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTAxMjI2MiwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMDk4NjYyfQ.GsFh9Dc1fEuu_ycUtey6rz6U32C6bAEP-58oRtgWtFPxxSXU31r6SMpessMEuelH

{
  "name": "City General",
  "totalBeds": 150,
  "latitude": 28.6139,
  "longitude": 77.2090
}

### EXPECTED: 403 Forbidden


### ==========================================
