### ==========================================

### 4A. Login as Admin (Copy the token!)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@mediflow.com",
  "password": "adminpassword"
}

### 4B. Admin accesses restricted endpoint
POST {{host}}/api/hospitals
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: 234546
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJyb2xlIjoiQURNSU4iLCJzdWIiOiIyIiwiaWF0IjoxNzgxNTEyMzc2LCJleHAiOjE3ODE1OTg3NzZ9.J3EVcQ_rn6RZB_7x4mu2Zgn3RVU3JI1B--pRm2tJnZYZRQX61CKypRY0K2dhhZFV

{
  "name": "City General",
  "totalBeds": 150,
  "latitude": 28.6139,
  "longitude": 77.2090
